aa(lp35
VSo then I was thinking to myself:
p36
aVIs this magic?
p37
aVHow does this work?
p38
aVAs geneticists would like you to think,
p39
aVperhaps the mother had the "bad mother" gene
p40
aVthat caused her pups to be stressful,
p41
aVand then it was passed from generation to generation;
p42
aVit's all determined by genetics.
p43
aVOr is it possible that something else is going on here?
